{"about_the_game":"<strong>Wilderness Calls!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Embark on an epic adventure in the wilderness, where you'll brandish an arsenal of unique weapons, clash with hordes of formidable enemies, and amass precious materials and gold coins.</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Steam-Title-Craft.png?t=1731316120\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL_-_Crafting_-_Steam_-_ENG.gif?t=1731316120\" /><br><strong>Gather</strong> wood to <strong>Build</strong> mighty <strong>Towers</strong> that will serve as your last line of defense. Use more wood to upgrade or repair towers. Or craft many bombs to BOOM enemies out of existence<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Steam-Title-Upgrades.png?t=1731316120\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL_-_Steam_-_Upgrades.gif?t=1731316120\" /><strong>Gold coins = EXP</strong>. <br><strong>Kill enemies</strong> to <strong>get coins</strong> to <strong>level up</strong> and buy stats, weapons, or buffs. Wield <strong>multiple weapons</strong> \u2014 melee, ranged, and magic. Upgrade weapons and spells to MAX and buy related BUFF to unlock S-Rank synergies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Steam-Titles_4_ENG.png?t=1731316120\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL_Day-Night_Steam.gif?t=1731316120\" /><br>Gather resources by <strong>DAY</strong>, when orcs target you. Protect the Moon Tower by <strong>NIGHT</strong> from the 4-side siege. During the day more resources appear, and orcs only target you. But during the night when the Moon Tower rises, orcs attack it and you need to <strong>build protective towers</strong> around it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Steam-Title-Animals.png?t=1731316120\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL_Steam_Animal.gif?t=1731316120\" /><strong>Take the lost animal running in circles to the teleport</strong> to escape the orc invasion. In return, <strong>they will grant you special gifts</strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Steam-Titles-Meta.png?t=1731316120\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/WL-Meta-Steam.gif?t=1731316120\" /><br>Kill Bosses and elites to get a chance to receive gems. Then spend gems to increase your stats OR buy new towers.<br><br><i>We took big inspiration from Brotato, Noobs want to live, and Don't Starve. If you like the results of our efforts, please wishlist the game!</i><br> - <br><br><i>*Wild Legion es parte de Erabit's Bud Scheme, un espacio para la creatividad de juegos y desarrolladores en solitario/equipos peque\u00f1os para prosperar.</i><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Die, tree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2359760/1c0b36d008c9b041dc93573b38a13c3181c57680.jpg"},{"name":"Will be of use","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2359760/53ae85eca29122b7432b05377d8aa4026de1057e.jpg"},{"name":"I plan to sell it later","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2359760/6295a1d7f120cef06f9b2e1aa8ac251746cc6c73.jpg"},{"name":"No more Amazon forest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2359760/42a31eabf707996eab87705ce098b99de5c34